  "texts": [
    "Table S6 shows the median pairwise distances between the nEMD of the various prompting strategies.",
    "It shows the interview and chat strategies give answers that are both similar to each other (median nEMD.01), and less similar to the first person strategy (.05).",
    "Put otherwise, different prompting strategies lead to different answers, although the differences may be small.",
    "Figure S12 shows a multidimensional scaling with WVS and LLMs responses from the three prompting strategies.",
    "We clearly see that the position of the answer patterns can differ, but that conclusions about the distance to the human response and the low adaptability of the LLM responses hold."
  ],
